{"tid":2435340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請還愛滋病一個清白","createTime":"2021-03-06T07:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T12:54:04.000Z","uid":267942,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1331014631082b33a20fe23c1495401d8709e5","tid":2435340,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"請還愛滋病一個清白<br />\n<br />\n多年來，好多人誤解愛滋病病毒會直接毒死人，<br />\n<br />\n其實咁多年來，從來冇一個人死直接死係愛滋病毒上面，<br />\n<br />\n請大家好好還愛滋病清白。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHIV並不能直接引起病症，但病毒進入人體後便侵襲人體免疫系統內的「T4細胞」（白血球細胞和巨噬細胞），使免疫系統和自行修補傷患的能力減弱。 這時，一些對未受感染人士沒有威脅的疾病如肺囊蟲肺炎等便能乘虛而入，使感染者發病轉為愛滋病病人。 現時雖然仍未有藥物能根治愛滋病病毒，但本港採用的療法，已大大將感染者壽命延長。"},{"pid":"119e8e245186fed1e4f55c96be887653a50f576e","tid":2435340,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"唔會直接但會間接"},{"pid":"b3032c56eb3ae23174a18581f43cbdfb8ea513b2","tid":2435340,"uid":267942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"話科興打死人，<br />\n<br />\n同話愛滋病毒毒死人一樣，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊樣難d?"},{"pid":"3d2485a46df4b023fcdf34a52d888cc5bbec007e","tid":2435340,"uid":256371,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"刀唔會殺人，只係個人失血先死<br />\nkid..."},{"pid":"f57308d9f2d61c8339d87e8a44c578ecc279dd7d","tid":2435340,"uid":392206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"肯定樓豬有愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9083c6a37f35945a5cb5ed0e839813c71cdd169c","tid":2435340,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"將全部有性病啲撚嘢拉哂去打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就可以瘋狂性交"},{"pid":"6c5d05ab6785b14dcb381b81fbf43cdb81701c98","tid":2435340,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57308d9f2d61c8339d87e8a44c578ecc279dd7d","tid":2435340,"uid":392206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c